This task explores how prompt design, tone, and examples influence creative outputs such as stories, startup ideas, or ad copy.
Creative Task: Generate a short story idea for a futuristic startup concept.

Basic	“Write a startup idea.”	
Refined	“Write a futuristic AI startup idea in 2050 that helps humans and robots live together peacefully.”	
Creative idea — “HarmonyTech: A company building empathy chips for robots.”
More imaginative — “DreamSync: AI startup that records dreams to help people overcome fears.”
